file_content.text: I didn't think anyone would be able to make it in here. Thank you.
When I get back to Sobrik, I'm jumping straight into a cockpit. The resistance is going to pay.
Thanks. That was a close call.
I thought I was dead for sure. Thank you.
Thanks for breaking me out of here. I won't forget it.
You came just in time--they said they were getting ready to execute me.
